This place rocks!!!... I read  few reviews before making reservation, I came in with my own bottle of water, no order bread, my waitress even advised me not to order too much & my bill came out so reasonable.  The dishes are outstanding, fresh seafood, the duck was sooo good.  I am coming back for 2nd time to complete my wished list.  So study its menu, prepare yourself, set your expectation, win-win for both sides.  Service excellent, outstanding foods!!!....
